structure.unit: JUVENILE PROCEEDINGS -- COMMITMENT AND CARE OF CHILDREN

law.history: Repealed 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 157, sec. 54, effective February 27, 1956. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 83, sec. 1, effective July 1, 1952.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Transfer of Child Welfare Division from Department of Economic Security to Kentucky Children's Bureau.
